1882044205138432310	Build human-like memory for your Agents!\n\nEvery agentic and RAG system struggles with real-time knowledge updates and fast data retrieval.\n\nZep AI solves these issues with its continuously learning and temporally-aware Knowledge Graph—think of it as human memory for AI Agents. https://t.co/QZIshV1ncR	2025-01-22 12:34:39	Akshay 🚀	akshay_pachaar	{}	{"name": "Akshay 🚀", "full_text": "Build human-like memory for your Agents!\\n\\nEvery agentic and RAG system struggles with real-time knowledge updates and fast data retrieval.\\n\\nZep AI solves these issues with its continuously learning and temporally-aware Knowledge Graph—think of it as human memory for AI Agents. https://t.co/QZIshV1ncR", "tweet_url": "https://x.com/akshay_pachaar/status/1882044205138432310", "tweeted_at": "2025-01-22T12:34:39.000Z", "screen_name": "akshay_pachaar", "extended_media": [{"url": "https://t.co/QZIshV1ncR", "type": "animated_gif", "sizes": {"large": {"h": 1036, "w": 1042, "resize": "fit"}, "small": {"h": 676, "w": 680, "resize": "fit"}, "thumb": {"h": 150, "w": 150, "resize": "crop"}, "medium": {"h": 1036, "w": 1042, "resize": "fit"}}, "id_str": "1882044197920030721", "indices": [278, 301], "media_key": "16_1882044197920030721", "video_info": {"variants": [{"url": "https://video.twimg.com/tweet_video/Gh5dOfybwAESuyn.mp4", "bitrate": 0, "content_type": "video/mp4"}], "aspect_ratio": [521, 518]}, "display_url": "pic.x.com/QZIshV1ncR", "expanded_url": "https://x.com/akshay_pachaar/status/1882044205138432310/photo/1", "media_results": {"result": {"media_key": "16_1882044197920030721"}}, "original_info": {"width": 1042, "height": 1036, "focus_rects": []}, "media_url_https": "https://pbs.twimg.com/tweet_video_thumb/Gh5dOfybwAESuyn.jpg", "ext_media_availability": {"status": "Available"}}], "note_tweet_text": "Build human-like memory for your Agents!\\n\\nEvery agentic and RAG system struggles with real-time knowledge updates and fast data retrieval.\\n\\nZep AI solves these issues with its continuously learning and temporally-aware Knowledge Graph—think of it as human memory for AI Agents.\\n\\nLike humans, Zep organizes an Agent's memories into episodes, extracts entities and their relationships from these episodes, and stores them in a knowledge graph:\\n\\n(refer the image below as you read)\\n\\n1️⃣ Episode Subgraph: Captures raw data with timestamps, retaining every detail for easy historical lookup.\\n\\n2️⃣ Semantic Entity Subgraph: Extracts entities (e.g., “Alice,” “Google”) and facts (“Alice works at Google”). Everything is versioned, so outdated info gets replaced.\\n\\n3️⃣ Community Subgraph: Groups related entities into clusters, with summaries for faster retrieval.\\n\\nZep delivers up to 18.5% higher accuracy with 90% lower latency when compared to tools like MemGPT.\\n\\nIt's fully open-source. I've shared a detailed paper with more information and their GitHub repository in next tweet!", "profile_image_url_https": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1578327351544360960/YFpWSWIX_normal.jpg"}	\N	\N
