ata access.\\n\\n10) Monitor, improve, and scale\\nUse analytics and feedback to refine memory systems and scale capabilities.\\n\\nThese steps provide a high-level guide for building stateful AI agents.\\n\\nIf you want to dive deeper into how memory works or integrating it, here's a great article: https://t.co/2Gy4AvbnkU\\n\\n💭 Over to you. Have you worked on projects with AI agents? 💬", "profile_image_url_https": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1614543077619953664/822_Gqfy_normal.jpg"}	\N	\N
